# Cursor reads .gitignore by default. Ephemeral workflow files below are
# gitignored (local/generated) but must stay visible to the agent for RPI
# continuity, session recovery, and adversarial review handoff.
#
# See: https://cursor.com/docs/reference/ignore-file

# Re-enable gitignored planning artifacts
!docs/planning_docs/session_state.json
!docs/planning_docs/review_context.json

# Ensure the full planning docs tree stays indexed (templates, sub-reports,
# adversarial_review.md, implementation_plan.md, etc.)
!docs/planning_docs/
!docs/planning_docs/**
